  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Chop onion and garlic finely.",
    "Heat oil in a pan, sauté onion until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add butternut squash, season with soy sauce, chicken broth concentrate, water, and optional shrimp paste. Stir well to combine.",
    "Pour mixture into a baking dish. Sprinkle soy milk evenly over the top of the soup.",
    "Bake in preheated oven until soup reaches desired consistency (about 20-30 minutes).",
